blogPost.excerpt: Codeprints offers geeky wall art for nerds and developers. You can create a personalized print of your GitHub contributions to motivate you every day. A service created for developers by developers.
blogPost.body: Codeprints offers geeky wall art for nerds and developers. You can create a personalized print of your GitHub contributions to motivate you every day. A service created for developers by developers.
blogPost.title: Codeprints - Your code is art - git contributions on your wall
blogPost.author: Wolfgang Gassler

localize.description: Codeprints为书呆子和开发者提供极客墙艺。你可以为你的GitHub贡献创建一个个性化的打印，以激励你每天。一个由开发者为开发者创建的服务。
localize.tagline: 你的代码就是艺术--git贡献在你的墙上。

localize.description: Codeprints爲書呆子和開發者提供極客牆藝。你可以爲你的GitHub貢獻創建一個個性化的打印，以激勵你每天。一個由開發者爲開發者創建的服務。
localize.tagline: 你的代碼就是藝術--git貢獻在你的牆上。
